    <pg ref="">
        <title><beast>The Python</beast></title>
        <fig>
            <img alt="The Python" src=""/>
        </fig>
        <lg>
            <l n="1">A <beast>Python</beast> I should not <act>advise</act>,—</l>
            <l n="2">It needs a <person>doctor</person> for its eyes,</l>
            <l n="3">And has the measles yearly.</l>
        </lg>
        <pgNum n="212">[212]</pgNum>
    </pg>
    <pg ref="">
        <fig>
            <img alt="Subject it to music" src=""/>
        </fig>
        <lg>
            <l n="1">However, if <person>you</person> feel inclined</l>
            <l n="2">To get one (to <act>improve your mind</act>,</l>
            <l n="3">And not from fashion merely),</l>
            <l n="4"><act>Allow no music </act><location>near its cage</location>;</l>
        </lg>
        <pgNum n="213">[213]</pgNum>
    </pg>
    <pg ref="">
        <fig>
            <img alt="Flies into a rage" src=""/>
        </fig>
        <lg>
            <l n="1">And when it <act>flies into a <emot>rage</emot></act></l>
            <l n="2"><act>Chastise</act> it, most severely.</l>
        </lg>
        <fig>
            <img alt="An aunt in Yucatan" src=""/>
        </fig>
        <pgNum n="214">[214]</pgNum>
    </pg>
    <pg ref="">
        <lg>
            <l n="1">I had an <person>aunt</person> in <location>Yucatan</location></l>
            <l n="2">Who <act>bought</act> a <beast>Python</beast> from a <person>man</person></l>
            <l n="3">And <act>kept it</act> for a <beast>pet</beast>.</l>
            <l n="4"><gen>She </gen><act>died</act>, because she <act>never knew</act></l>
            <l n="5">These simple little rules and few;—</l>
        </lg>
        <pgNum n="215">[215]</pgNum>
    </pg>
    <pg ref="">
        <fig>
            <img alt="The snake" src=""/>
        </fig>
        <lg>
            <l n="1">The <beast>Snake</beast> is <act>living</act> yet.</l>
        </lg>
        <pgNum n="216">[216]</pgNum>
    </pg>
